SELECT ?diseaseGroupLabel WHERE {
  cell:cell_HPS0929 brs:brs_derivedFrom ?intermediate .
  ?intermediate <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000050> cell:cell_Donor_HPS0929 .
  cell:cell_Donor_HPS0929 cell:cell_0000054 ?diseaseGroup .

}
